Corruption
EXPOSED: Speaker Of Lagos Assembly, Obasa, Awards Contracts To Self Through Company Registered In Son's Name
0 Comments
1 Day Ago With reports by SaharaReporters exposing some of the shady deals of the Speaker and his surrogate companies, the panic button was pressed by Obasa. He was reported to have urgently mobilised some members of the GAC to convene the meeting and intervene to save his seat. SaharaReporters had published a report highlighting a list of companies the Speaker had been using to award contracts to himself and launder public funds. To avoid a direct linking to himself, Obasa did not use his name to register but used his father, wife and children as shareholders in the company. 



